I spoke a little with Paul who is some what cast down without knowing what
the D said, he wish God woold make it short with him. The illness woold be
little troubel if he had peace and joy in the Lord. We have to wait and
with Gods grace we will quietly wait opon Him who has never failed to His
promises. I wish you a good time Try to hear something about Mrs Hoch eyes.
Love to all
.fo -
